msgid ""
"Koko is trying to replicate the recipe for\n"
"her mother's beloved honeyed apples,\n"
"but she's missing the essential\n"
"<1.se_co>courser bee honey<2.re_co>. The <3.se_co>courser bees<4.re_co>\n"
"are found in dangerous territory outside\n"
"of the village, beyond her reach..."
msgstr ""

